can I get pub manager please?

Thanks for reaching out! At the moment, dedicated account management is reserved for advertisers who meet a daily spend threshold of $1,000 or more. If you’re not at that level yet, no worries — our self-serve platform has everything you need to launch and optimize your campaigns successfully. Our support team is also available via chat or email if you need any help. Let me know if there’s anything else I can assist you with!
how long pending status will be?

Ad approval typically takes around 4 hours on weekdays and up to 8 hours on weekends. If your ad is still pending, it might be due to a new account verification. Could you please provide the following details for verification? 
- Company's full address
- Company's legal entity name
- Account Email
- Company's EHID or DUNS number
- Primary contact person's name
- Company's phone number
Once you have this information, please email adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification. This will help us expedite the process.
Could you please provide the ad ID you're referring to? This will help me assist you better with your pending ad status.
